node.text:
Frank Frazetta’s 𝑫𝒆𝒂𝒕𝒉 𝑫𝒆𝒂𝒍𝒆𝒓 is making his debut in the blockchain gaming world of the VulcanVerse as a 1 of 1 NFT playable character in game brought to you by @frazettagirls. The VulcanVerse @vulcan_verse is a massive multiplayer online role-playing game (MMORPG) set in a Greco-Roman fantasy world made up of 10,000 plots of land (NFTs), divided over 4 quadrants: Arcadia, Notus, Hades and Boreas. The lore and characters are written by Fighting Fantasy authors, who are currently producing 5 game books for the VulcanVerse. The game incorporates an intricate sandbox building system, quests and battles and defi of being able to earn while staking in the land. Over 500 prizes will be raffled including the 1 of 1 playable NFT 𝑫𝒆𝒂𝒕𝒉 𝑫𝒆𝒂𝒍𝒆𝒓 character, 𝑫𝒆𝒂𝒕𝒉 𝑫𝒆𝒂𝒍𝒆𝒓weapons and armor, posters and more!
.
.
The winning tickets for the top three prizes will be drawn live on the VulcanVerse twitch live stream, By The Fire, Friday 30th July 8pm GMT, 1pm EST. No crypto currency required to participate. Visit frazetta.vulcanverse.com to purchase tickets for the raffle!
.
.
.
.
.
.
#FrazettaGirls #DeathDealer #FrankFrazetta #Frazetta #FantasyArt #VulcanVerse #NFTGaming
